Technique Benefit Notes File compaction Fewer paths, faster scans Run periodically Z-ordering Better predicate pruning Use on high-selectivity columns Caching Faster repeated queries Use sparingly <p>tip</p> <p>You can define table properties to lift performance</p> <pre><code>ALTER TABLE silver.orders SET TBLPROPERTIES (
  'delta.autoOptimize.autoCompact' = 'true',
  'delta.autoOptimize.optimizeWrite' = 'true'
);
